  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p828581/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p828581/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/09/26/3b7ee2340c743657566d30a9bd437035.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p828581\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t（先按白色播放键，再按黄色播放键，才能收听哦。）</p>\n<p>\n\t本文声优：FISH</p>\n<p>\n\tAll the Difference in The World<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">整个世界因你而改变</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Every Sunday morning I take a light&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/jog\" target=\"_blank\">jog</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;around a park near my home.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">There&rsquo;s a lake located in one corner of the park. Each time I jog by this lake, I see the same elderly woman sitting at the water&rsquo;s edge with a small metal cage sitting beside her.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">每个星期日的早晨我都会绕着我家附近的公园轻松地慢跑。公园的一角有一片湖。每当我慢跑经过这片湖，都会看到同一个老妇人，身边放着一个金属笼子坐在湖边。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">This past Sunday my&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/curiosity\" target=\"_blank\">curiosity</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;got the best of me, so I stopped jogging and walked over to her.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">上个星期日我终于忍不住好奇，停止了慢跑，走到她身边。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tAs I got closer, I realized that the metal cage was in fact a small trap.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">走近时我发现金属笼子其实是一个小陷阱。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tThere were three turtles, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unharmed\" target=\"_blank\">unharmed</a>, slowly walking around the base of the trap.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">三只乌龟安然无恙，绕着陷阱底部慢悠悠地爬着。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t[ls]She had a fourth turtle in her lap that she was carefully <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scrub\" target=\"_blank\">scrubbing</a> with a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/spongy\" target=\"_blank\">spongy</a> brush.[/ls]<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">她正认真地用海绵刷擦拭着第四只趴在她膝盖上的乌龟。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Hello,&rdquo; I said. &ldquo;If you don&rsquo;t mind my <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nosiness\" target=\"_blank\">nosiness</a>, I&rsquo;d love to know what you&rsquo;re doing with these turtles.&rdquo;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;你好啊，&rdquo;我说。&ldquo;如果你不介意我多管闲事的话，我很想知道你在对这些乌龟做什么呢。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\tShe smiled. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m cleaning off their shells ,&rdquo; she replied.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;我在清洗他们的壳，&rdquo;她笑着回答说。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Anything on a turtle&rsquo;s shell, like <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/algae\" target=\"_blank\">algae</a> or <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scum\" target=\"_blank\">scum</a>, reduces the turtle&rsquo;s ability to absorb heat and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/impede\" target=\"_blank\">impedes</a> its ability to swim. It can also <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/corrode\" target=\"_blank\">corrode</a> and weaken the shell over time.&rdquo;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">任何乌龟壳上，像海藻、泡沫浮渣这些东西，都会减弱乌龟的吸热能力并且阻碍他们游动，时间长了还会腐蚀龟壳，让龟壳变得脆弱。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tShe went on: &ldquo;I spend a couple of hours each Sunday morning, relaxing by this lake and helping these little guys out. It&rsquo;s my own strange way of making a difference.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">她继续说道：&ldquo;每个星期天早晨我都会花几个小时待在湖边，边放松自己，边帮这些小家伙摆脱困难。这就是我奇怪的制造改变的方式。&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;But don&rsquo;t most freshwater turtles live their whole lives with&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">algae</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;and scum hanging from their shells?&rdquo; I asked.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;但是，难道不是所有的淡水乌龟都是伴随着它们壳上的海藻和泡沫、浮渣度过一生的吗？&rdquo;我问道。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;Yep, sadly, they do,&rdquo; she replied.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;遗憾的是，它们的确这样。&rdquo;她回答道。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;Well then, don&rsquo;t you think your time could be better spent? And 99% of these turtles don&rsquo;t have kind people like you to help them clean off their shells. So, no offense&hellip; but how exactly are your&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/localized\" target=\"_blank\">localized</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;efforts here truly making a difference?&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;那么，你不觉得你在浪费时间吗？99%的乌龟都没有遇到像你这么好的人去帮他们清洗龟壳。所以，无意冒犯&hellip;但是你在这儿，通过你一个人的努力到底能带来多大改变呢？&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\tThe woman <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/giggle\" target=\"_blank\">giggled</a> aloud.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">老妇人大声咯咯笑起来。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tShe then looked down at the turtle in her lap, scrubbed off the last piece of algae from its shell, and said, &ldquo;Sweetie, if this little guy could talk, he&rsquo;d tell you I just made all the difference in the world.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">接着她看看膝盖上的乌龟，把龟壳上的最后一块海藻擦拭干净，说道：&ldquo;亲爱的，如果这只小乌龟会说话的话，它一定会告诉你我刚刚改变了整个世界。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p828581/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p828581\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p905050/\">史上最糟糕的学习方法，你中招了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p910656/\">囧研究：哪国人英语最烂？我被结果惊呆了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p901286/\">老外听力考试遇上神曲《江南皮革厂倒闭了》，听完都懵了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p807754/\">2016年下半年英语四级口语考试9大复习方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p901201/\">双语美文：别急于做判断，这样才能看得真切</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p906901/\">奥巴马真认可川普当总统？白宫会晤意味深长</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p906881/\">哈里王子为女票发声明怒怼媒体！男友力爆棚！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p870842/\">工作腻了想跳槽？这些建议值得一看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p905037/\">普京恭贺川普当选总统的这通电话 字字有玄机</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p908748/\">加州要闹独立了？川普上位的冲击力果然不小</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
